resources.string: Siyabonga ngesibuyekezo sakho, futhi sicela usinikeze impendulo ethile.
Uma usilinganisela, singakuthokozela kakhulu futhi sizoqhubeka nokusebenza kanzima ukuze sikunikeze umuzwa ongcono.
Sicela usazise nganoma yiziphi izinkinga ohlangabezane nazo.
Sicela unikeze imininingwane eyengeziwe ukuze usisize sikhombe futhi sixazulule inkinga yakho ngokushesha okukhulu (ubuncane bezinhlamvu ezingu-6).
Sizoyilungisa le nkinga enguqulweni ezayo. Ngiyaxolisa ngesiphazamiso
Ayikwazi ukuthola uhlelo lokusebenza ku-Google Play
